2023 changed my life ❤️ I’m forever grateful for the adventures and lessons learned this year. Here’s a couple of special moments.

1. February - Started touring North America with @djpressplay & @wasted.willy (my first taste of touring in years and with one of the best groups of guys out there)

2. April - Went to space

3. May - Performed at my first festival with DJ Press Play and it was a movie

4. My mom after @hermanli asked me to tour with DragonForce ❤️

5. July - Watched the sunset on a boat

6. August - My first solo show in LA opening for @marcusveltri and @rob_landes (we also filmed some epic vids during this trip that went pretty viral!)

7. September - Practicing for DragonForce tour and filming videos to backlog for the rest of the year for YouTube. it was really tough but I haven’t had to film videos since because I backlogged so much 😅

8. ❤️❤️❤️

9. October - @dragonforcehq North American tour begins (my first time ever living on a tour bus. Met so many of my guitar hero’s and made so many amazing friends along the way. Also ate beef jerky for the first time thanks to @geeanzalone and I’m now addicted 😂) 

10. Hard work paying off and dreams coming true ❤️

On tour with @dragonforcehq 🎤🎸
